	<message label="045_01_02" attrib="00 00 00"><20_3 arg="6" />那麼，<tag a="110" b="1" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />就是
