	<message label="045_04_01" attrib="00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於決定好島的名字了。<delay40 />
