	<message label="045_04_02" attrib="00 00 00">各位，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都拿好杯子了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是用<tag a="110" b="1" />
